# This directory stores serialized model artifacts generated by backend/src/train.py:
#   - modelo_defasagem.pkl  (trained RandomForest)
#   - colunas.pkl           (list of feature column names)
#   - metricas.json         (ROC-AUC and accuracy logged at training time)
#
# Run `python backend/src/train.py` to generate these files before building the Docker image.
